'''''Diplomat''''', '''October 1966''' is a magazine which includes the article "[[Tolkien on Tolkien]]" (p. 39). The magazine features a Tolkien-inspired cover illustration by Barry Geller.<ref>''An Illustrated Tolkien Bibliography'' at Tolkienbooks.net</ref>
